ATTRIBUTION / PROVENANCE

The patched JavaScript files under `docker-build/` (session.js, types.js,
station.js, eufysecurity.js) are MODIFIED build artifacts of
eufy-security-client by bropat <patrick.broetto@gmail.com>, distributed under
the MIT License: https://github.com/bropat/eufy-security-client

The Dockerfile builds on the official image
`bropat/hassio-eufy-security-ws-amd64:2.1.0` from
https://github.com/bropat/hassio-eufy-security-ws

The HomeBase 3 fix is based on, and extends, the unmerged upstream
PR #888: https://github.com/bropat/eufy-security-client/pull/888

This repository is an independent community patch and is not affiliated with
or endorsed by Anker/Eufy or bropat.
